verbose_text: These results suggested that HOXC10 interacts with PRMT5, which promotes H3R2me1 and H3R2me2s enrichment on the VEGFA promoter and recruits WDR5 for subsequent methylation of H3K4 at the VEGFA promoter, eventually resulting in VEGFA transcription.
